WS Elastic Beanstalk is an easy-to-use service for deploying and scaling web applications and services developed with various programming languages. You can simply upload your code and Elastic Beanstalk automatically handles the deployment, from capacity provisioning, load balancing, auto-scaling to application health monitoring. Elastic Beanstalk is covered under AWS Shield Standard. Advanced coverage is not offered for this service.</p>\n<p>Reference:\n  <a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/waf/latest/developerguide/ddos-overview.html\">https://docs.aws.amazon.com/waf/latest/developerguide/ddos-overview.html</a></p>\n</div></div>]",
